Posts.Content: I was not sure where to post this, since I dont know what it is. My left breast near my underarm has had a lump, but not like a circular lump feels more like a tube shaped lump on my breast, my dr did a ulrasound after the other test came back normal and see's nothing but she still wants me to see a specialist re this, has anyone had somehting similar to this? any info will help!
